data.description: Welcome to this adorable 3 bed/2 bath cottage in SW Atlanta! Fully renovated just a few years ago, this spacious open concept home features a bright chef's kitchen (literally, owned by a chef!) with stainless appliances, recessed lighting, and granite counters uniquely designed to entertain with seating all around.  Beautiful hardwood floors throughout. Large living space and dining area with French doors opening to a nice deck overlooking the private fenced backyard.  The peaceful owners suite, tucked away perfectly from the rest of the home, is spacious with two closets and a tranquil spa like bathroom. The additional two bedrooms are also generous in size.  Prime location just minutes away from the Beltline, Monday Night Garage, Boxcar, the new Lee White Food Hall, shopping, Marta and much more!
